pull.title: Handle rename failure in DumpMempool(...) by using the RenameOver(...) return value. Add [[nodiscard]] to RenameOver(...).
pull.body:
Handle rename failure in `DumpMempool(...)` by using the `RenameOver(...)` return value.

Add `[[nodiscard]]` to `RenameOver(...)` to reduce the risk of similar rename issues in the future.

events.message: Handle rename failure in DumpMempool(...) by using RenameOver(...) return value

events.body:
ACK ce9dd454

This was the only place where the return value of `RenameOver()` was not inspected.

Would be useful to print the reason for the rename failure, but that's out of the scope of this PR.
